OL,5, A landlord who saw six of his rented   
OL,6, properties flooded by sewage water has 
OL,7, accused a utilities company of a       
OL,8, "catastrophic failure".                
OL,10,FStewart Hamilton waited more than three
OL,11,Fweeks for effective repairs to be      
OL,12,Fcarried out on a blocked drain near the
OL,13,Fflats in Eastbourne, East Sussex.      
OL,15,FHe said the leaks began just before    
OL,16,FChristmas and were fixed on Saturday.  
OL,18,FSouthern Water (SW) apologised and said
OL,19,Fthere was "no excuse" for why the      
OL,20,Frepairs had taken "so long".           
